</details>
<br><br>

**استخراج الطرق الكاتبية:**
<div dir="ltr">

```python
from adab import adab

# جميعها
resutl = adab.writing_types()
print("All", resutl, sep="\n\n", end="\n\n")

# عبر الايدي
resutl = adab.writing_types(type_id=15)
print("By id", resutl, sep="\n\n", end="\n\n")
```
